Project: Communicate Data Findings (Dataset: Loan Data from prosper)¶

by Saphal Adhikari¶

Preliminary Wrangling¶

The Dataset contains 113,917 loans, each row include infomation on the borrow's APR, status, borrowed amount, debt, etc. This investigation will be analyzing factors that influence borrow's APR and how each loan were taken by what type of borrowers.

What is the structure of your dataset?¶

This dataset contain 113,937 loans with 81 features.we can see more variable are in numeric form.Each loan contain information on the borrowered's background information and details regarding the loans.

What is/are the main feature(s) of interest in your dataset?¶

I'm looking forward for f the borrower's Annual Percentage Rate (APR) also I am more interested on finding the borrower's rating, score, occupation and income that could influence change in borrower's APR.

What features in the dataset do you think will help support your investigation into your feature(s) of interest?¶

I think loan amount will have impact on APR and also i am interested in borrower's monthly income. loan term, rating and job status, monthly payment. Let's find out if this will impact our data or not.I would like to look at following features:

  1. ProsperScore
  2. BorrowerRate
  3. Loan status
  4. Total Prosper Bill Payed
  5. Income
  6. Employment
  7. Occupation
